Package: BusinessReport
Type: Package
Title: Professional Business Report Templates for Quarto/Typst
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given  = "First",
      family = "Last",
      email  = "your@email.com",
      role   = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")
    )
  )
Description: Provides professional Quarto report templates rendered via Typst
    for business, analytical, and technical reporting. Features include optional
    cover and back cover pages, a curated collection of fonts from renowned
    publications and open-source typeface projects, and three distinct table of
    contents styles (classic, modern, and minimal). Reports are created as
    self-contained Quarto projects that users can version-control and extend.
